Title: Day 5: 11:00 P.M. - 12:00 A.M.
Plot:
Jack and Wayne locate a recording that definitively proves Logan's involvement in the terrorist conspiracy, but Henderson corners them in the hopes of destroying the incriminating tape. 

Logan tries to cover his tracks by issuing a warrant for Jack's arrest. 

Audrey contacts her father for help, while Chloe gives her cover while helping Jack evade CTU.
GuestStars: William Devane,  Jenny Levine,  Skylar Roberge,  Jason Grutter,  Addie Daddio,  Jeff Campbell,  Jorge Noa,  Rick Garcia,  Brandon Ford Green,  John Posey
